Our data concerns dragonflies diversity collected from 1946 to 1958 and hold at Parc Botanique et Zoologique de Tsimbazaza, Madagascar. This is the first published record at this collection. This data was published to make data available, accessible and useful for biodvidersity conservation.|378 occurrences
